     * Places characters of &lt;var&gt;cadena&lt;/var&gt; in a matrix with &lt;var&gt;numberOfColumnsInMatrix&lt;/var&gt;
     * columns and as many rows as required in order to hold all characters of &lt;var&gt;cadena&lt;/var&gt;.
